descp2: Specifies the reduction to apply to the output: `'none'` | `'batchmean'` | `'sum'` | `'mean'`. `'none'`: no reduction will be applied. `'batchmean'`: the sum of the output will be divided by batchsize. `'sum'`: the output will be summed. `'mean'`: the output will be divided by the number of elements in the output. Default: `'mean'`
